<h2>Results: What to Expect</h2>
<p>After completing these 7 steps, here is a realistic timeline:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Immediately:</strong> Your website and profiles show correct information. Any human checking your details finds accurate data</li>
<li><strong>2-4 weeks:</strong> Perplexity (which does real-time web search) begins showing corrected information</li>
